title: Cheeto that looks like Harambe sold for nearly $100K on eBay
text:
A Cheeto that bears a resemblance to Harambe, a slain gorilla that has become fodder for internet jokes since his death last May , has sold for nearly $100,000 on eBay.
The seller said he found the cheese snack in a bag of Flamin' Hot Cheetos. Bidding began at $11.99 on Jan. 28. It ended early Tuesday morning with a winning bid of $99,900. The listing showed a picture of the Cheeto side-by-side with a gorilla climbing a tree.
» Harambe’s grandmother euthanized at age 49
Last May, Harambe was shot by handlers at the Cincinnati Zoo after dragging a small boy who had gotten into his enclosure.
